---
import SiteLayout from '@layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
const title = `Home | Mille's Corner`;
---

<style>
  ul#spreadsheet-links a {
    @apply link-primary;
  }
</style>

<SiteLayout title={title} opengraph={{ title: 'Spreadsheet Links' }}>
  <main class="prose mx-auto max-w-3xl py-8 px-4 sm:px-8">
    <section class="card bg-base-200 p-8 md:p-12">
      <h1>Info</h1>
      <p>
        Hey, Mille here! I made a spreadsheet then I made another then another.
        There was an entire network of them, but most of them have fallen out of relevance in the current game state.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-2">
        If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to me on Bluesky (<a
          href="https://bsky.app/profile/millemarteaux.bsky.social"
          class="link link-hover link-secondary">millemarteaux.bsky.social</a
        >). The only stupid question is one not asked.<br>
        I'm also technically always <a
          class="link link-accent"
          href="/sandbird">recruiting for an alliance as well</a
        > if that interests you.
      </p>
      <h2 class="mb-0">Spreadsheet Links:</h2>
      <ul id="spreadsheet-links">
        <li>
          <h3>Gear Comparisons</h3>
          <a href="/weapons">Weapons and Armors</a>
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Calculators</h3>
          <a href="/damagecalculator">Damage Calculator</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Other</h3>
          <a href="/gptree">Global GP Tree schedule</a> (by @TheuberClips on Twitter)<br><a href="/dextbase">Dext Base N-Meseta farm</a><br><a href="/screenshottags">Commonly used Twitter/Bluesky hashtags for PSO2 screenshots</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>PSO2 Classic stuff</h3>
          <a href="/classicpse">How PSE works in PSO2 (and debunking rumors)</a> | <a href="/anchors">Divide Quest anchoring</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="divider my-16"></div>

    <section class="prose card max-w-full bg-base-200 p-8 md:p-12" id="about">
      <h1 class="">Yo~!</h1>
      <h2 class="mt-0">
        <a
          href="https://twitter.com/jojobii_"
          class="link link-hover link-secondary">@jojobii</a
        >
        here...
      </h2>
      <p>
        <a
          href="https://twitter.com/mille_pso2"
          class="link link-hover link-secondary">@mille_pso2</a
        >
        said it'd be cool to have a more presentable hub for their resources for
        <em
          >The Hit Action MMORPG
          <a href="https://ngs.pso2.com/" class="link link-hover link-accent"
            >Phantasy Star Online 2: New Genesis</a
          >
        </em>, so we're working on this together :3
      </p>
      <p>
        Typos or suggestions? Reach out to me on Twitter (<a
          href="https://twitter.com/jojobii_"
          class="link link-hover link-secondary">@jojobii</a
        >) or file an Issue on the <a
          class="link link-hover link-secondary"
          href="https://github.com/arks-moe/site-mille">GitHub Repo</a
        >!
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
